questions.quote: I just-I don't want us to jump into something we're not ready for.
So? Come on! Explain yourself Geller! First you get my Rachel pregnant!
Oh. Okay. Ooh! Ooh! Okay, maybe I'll talk about London! Y'know when you two hooked up! Only, only I won't say hooked up. I'll say, "Began their beautiful journey..."
You know honey, there is a thin line between love and hate, and it turns out that line...is a scarf!
Ok, ok, Roger was creepy, but he was nothing compared to Pete Carney.
No, it's good, it is good, it's just that- mm- doesn't she seem a little angry?
Okay, two things didn't happen. Remember I told you that someone made out with Ralph Lauren in the copy room? Well, it turns out that's not true.
...Couldn't enjoy a cup of noodles after that. I mean, is that ridiculous? Can you believe she actually thought that?
Yeah, I gotta go! I got an acting job. Like you'd believe that. This sucks!
I wanna sleep, I wanna eat, I wanna take a shower, I mean before she wakes up and we gotta do this all over again.
